                    <a href="https://my.yocoboard.com" style="background-color: #bf001b;background-image: linear-gradient(to right,#f34b58,#bf001b);font-size: 14px;color: #fff;padding: 8px 20px;border: none;border-radius: 100px;text-decoration: none;">Dashboard</a>
