                    <h3 style="font-size:20px;color:#4a4a4a;margin: 0 0 40px 0">Your Time-Trackers's Top Features:</h3>
                    <div style="background: url(https://my.yocoboard.com/min-images/png/peers-updates.png) right center no-repeat; height:170px;padding-right: 320px;font-family: Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom: 60px">
