                        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#6e6e6e;line-height:22px">Generate a comprehensive report of the time tracked for a team member in just a click. Filter your results and get downloadable reports to meet your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: url(https://my.yocoboard.com/min-images/png/profitability.png) right center no-repeat; height:170px;padding-right: 320px;font-family: Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom: 60px">
                        <h6 style="font-size:14px;color:#4a4a4a;font-weight: 600;margin:0 0 12px 0">Identify Profitablity</h6>
                        <hr style="margin: 0;background-color: #F04955;height: 1px;width: 60px;border: none;">
                        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#6e6e6e;line-height:22px">Smart reports measure project-based productivity and profitability. Enable tracking for each project and client.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: url(https://my.yocoboard.com/min-images/png/integrations.png) left center no-repeat; height:170px;padding-left: 320px;font-family: Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom: 60px">
                        <h6 style="font-size:14px;color:#4a4a4a;font-weight: 600;margin:0 0 12px 0">Integrations</h6>
                        <hr style="margin: 0;background-color: #F04955;height: 1px;width: 60px;border: none;">
                        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#6e6e6e;line-height:22px">Enhance time-tracking with smart and powerful integrations. Integrate YoCoBoard with apps like Slack, Zendesk, Trello and more.</p>
