                        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#6e6e6e;line-height:22px">Carry your time-tracker in your pocket and work anywhere. Clock-in and Clock-out of your projects with our Android and iOS apps.</p>
                        <div>
                            <a href= "https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/yocoboard-online-time-tracking-app/id980537651" style="background: url(~$[>DOMAIN_IMAGE<]$~min-images/png/app-store.png) no-repeat; width:83px; height:28px; display:inline-block;"></a>
